{"tid":2058020,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【第40期牆紙】一年","createTime":"2020-06-10T00:11:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-14T09:33:43.000Z","uid":253119,"like":38,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"fe9a57da493cb34c7c321b06badfbc8697c9da73","tid":2058020,"uid":253119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T00:11:48.000Z","msg":"整整一年，屢被打壓，受盡煎熬，但情感連繫起素未謀面的你我，創造了屬於我們的共同記憶。這場抗爭是一場持久戰，可能要窮盡你我一生。故不遺忘痛苦的回憶，便是對抗極權的一種。<br />\n<br />\n這一期，牆紙會和大家回顧及反省過去一年的抗爭現象，並思考如何裝備自己，做好長期抗爭的準備。<br />\n<br />\n縱使不知眼前路，但只要與你同行，便有決心繼續前行。<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n目錄<br />\n1. 40期&mdash;編者的話<br />\n2. 被打壓、思考、不投降 曾志豪：港人會繼續叫口號<br />\n3. 論情感與集體行動<br />\n4. 悼念的意義<br />\n5. Roaring by the Window<br />\n6. 兩種心態：鐵般堅持，血般堅決<br />\n7. 教育的啟迪<br />\n8. 持久戰&mdash;大家都能輕鬆做的10件事<br />\n9. 購買力令黃色經濟圈成長<br />\n10. 致Land of the Free，突破宿命的情書<br />\n11. 投稿&mdash;和你抗爭，我很愉快<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n點擊連結用投稿衝擊牆紙：@wallpaperneedyou<br />\n<br />\n#40th #40期<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ECuNaiS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FECuNaiS.jpg&h=bd78b8b8&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1KUQSxe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1KUQSxe.jpg&h=a598e2b3&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oWf1eLA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoWf1eLA.jpg&h=3fda1e4e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/N9YezLC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FN9YezLC.jpg&h=a1fe8bc5&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dzmcmqD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdzmcmqD.jpg&h=51b9a7d6&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/o40HJDZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/th